      "note": "summary",
      "abstract": "Homestead Exemption and Public Safety Funding;  Proposes amendments to State Constitution to revise homestead exemption, limit annual inflation adjustment, require funding for public safety remain at current levels, & require trust fund to provide supplemental funding to replace lost revenues."
    }
